import { Nav, Container, Image, Row, Col, Form, NavDropdown, Navbar, Button, NavLink, Card } from "react-bootstrap";
import logo from './img/logo.svg';
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
import { faBars, faMagnifyingGlass, faCircleUser,faDiscord } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';

const HeaderApp = () => {
    return (
        <Container fluid>
            <Navbar>
                <NavLink to='/'><Image className="logo_size" src={logo}></Image></NavLink>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbarScroll" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse className="navbarScroll">
                        <Nav
                            style={{ justifyContent: 'space-between' }}
                            navbarScroll
                        >

                            <Nav.Link to='/'>News</Nav.Link>
                            <NavDropdown title="Category" id="navbarScrollingDropdown">
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action3">PC</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action4">Mobile</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action4">Console</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action5">
                                    All
                                </NavDropdown.Item>
                            </NavDropdown>
                            <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faDiscord} /><Nav.Link to='/'>Join Discord</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link to='/'>About us</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                        {/* <Form className="d-flex">
                            <Form.Control
                                type="search"
                                placeholder="Search"
                                className="me-2"
                                aria-label="Search"
                                style={{ marginLeft: '300px' }}
                            />
                            <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
                        </Form> */}
                        <Nav style={{marginLeft:'300px'}}>
                        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMagnifyingGlass} className="icon_size" />
                        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCircleUser} className="icon_size" />
                        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faBars} className="icon_size" />
                        </Nav>

                    </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Navbar>
        </Container>

    );
};
export default HeaderApp;
